FBIS3-17982 "drsov062_f_94011" FBIS-SOV-94-062 Document Type:Daily Report 29 Mar 1994 National Affairs Meshkov Issues Decree on National Minorities Law LD3003210494 Kiev UNIAR in Ukrainian 2245 GMT 29 Mar 94 LD3003210494 Kiev UNIAR Language: Ukrainian Article Type:BFN [Text] Simferopol, 29 Mar--Crimean President Yuriy Meshkov has issued a decree on a mechanism to implement the law on national minorities. In accordance with the decree, a commission has been set up that is to prepare materials on implementing the rights of citizens to have their national surnames, first names, and patronymics, and to restore their nationality in documents. Anife Seytomer-Kyzy, adviser to the president of Crimea on international relations, is head of the commission.
